description:
This app allows you to collectively launch some of WebOS's most important apps all in one screen. Proven to be faster than opening each app individuality, Extreme Launcher can open many apps at your fingertips with a neat OS. NOTE! Updates are coming, I have read the reviews and will becoming out with an update based on the reviews shortly. Download while its free!
Like free apps? Help support with other apps too!
Check out other great apps by KDB Productions like Love Test!, Finger Print Scanner!, Dictionary FREE!, Extreme Launcher, Shut up!, and The Ultimate Strobe Light!
